data.name: pattern_new_text
data.value:
h1.#if($FEED_TYPE == "feed")Nov dogodek dodan: "$Caption":"$URL"
$Date "$UserName":"$UserURL" je dodal nov dogodek: "$Caption":"$URL"
$Text
"Preberi več":"$URL"
#end#if($FEED_TYPE == "poll")Nova anketa dodana: "$Caption":"$URL"ž
$Date "$UserName":"$UserURL" je dodal novo anketo: "$Caption":"$URL"
#foreach($Answer v $Answers)
#each
* $Answer
#end
"Vote":"$URL"
#end
^To e-pošto prejemate, ker ste registriran uporabnik "${__VirtualRootPath}":"${__VirtualRootPath}" portala. Če ne želite prejemati obvestil o novo dodanih dogodkih, prosim uredite svoje "nastavitve naročnine":"$RecipientSubscriptionConfigURL".^ Alternative translation

$Date "$UserName":"$UserURL" je dodal nov dogodek k "$Caption":"$URL" #if($FEED_TYPE == "poll")poll#end#if($FEED_TYPE == "feed")event#end:

^To e-pošto prejemate, ker ste registriran uporabnik "${__VirtualRootPath}":"${__VirtualRootPath}" portala. Če ne želite prejemati obvestil o novo dodanih komentarjih dodanih k dogodku, prosim uredite svoje "nastavitve naročnine":"$RecipientSubscriptionConfigURL".^
